/page A4 --landscape

/hero --bg gradient {
  # Annual Report 2024

  Building the future, one document at a time.

  /button primary "Download PDF"
  /button secondary "View Online"
}

/columns 2 -g 3rem {
  /region {
    ## Financial Highlights

    /columns 2 -g 1rem {
      /card {
        /text "$42M" --bold --size 2.5rem --color #059669

        Revenue
      }

      /card {
        /text "+32%" --bold --size 2.5rem --color #059669

        YoY Growth
      }
    }

    Revenue grew **32%** year over year, driven by strong performance
    in our cloud division and expanded enterprise partnerships.

    Our strategic initiatives in document automation have positioned
    us as a leader in the content creation space.
  }

  /region {
    ## Looking Forward

    Our roadmap for 2025 includes:

    - **AI Integration**: Smart content suggestions
    - **Collaboration**: Real-time multi-user editing
    - **Enterprise**: Advanced security and compliance

    /quote pull "The future of documents is programmable."
  }
}

/region --bg #1e3a5f --padding 3rem {
  /center {
    /text "Ready to transform your document workflow?" --color white --size 1.5rem

    /button primary "Contact Sales"
  }
}
